{"tid":769379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼龍目島7.0強震增至142死 數千房屋毀損旅遊區震散","createTime":"2018-08-06T06:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T16:35:45.000Z","uid":1221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f82981ada43c72121e68a994be957788c256d9fe","tid":769379,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180806/large/1533522219_69ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180806%2Flarge%2F1533522219_69ed.jpg&h=fae8e662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼旅遊勝地龍目島（Lombok Island）周日晚發生黎克特制6.9級強烈地震，官員指死亡人數增至142人，數百人受傷，初步相信無外國旅客身亡，但道路受損令近700名遊客被困。數以千計建築物夷為平地，由於很多災區仍未開始救援，預計死亡人數會進一步上升。另外。當局為安全計已派船赴龍目島對開的吉利群島協助疏散旅客。中國大使館證實200多名中國人滯留當地，當中包括港人。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國地質勘探局的報告，這次地震震央位於龍目島北部Loloan地區東南東外2公里處，震源深度只有10.5公里。當局一度發出海嘯警告，有地區出現高半米的浪。當局錄得至少21次餘震，最強一次達5.6級。<br />\n印尼國家災害應變總署發言人蘇托波（Sutopo Purwo Nugroho）表示，死傷最慘重是龍目島西、北部地區。死者包括一名1歲大嬰兒和一名72歲長者。印尼西努沙登加拉省（West Nusa Tenggara）災難管理中心主管羅姆（Muhammad Rum）表示，死者多數被跌下來的瓦礫擊中身亡。<br />\n地震導致多幢建築受損，幾千人逃離家園到戶外暫避。北龍目區首長納伊穆爾（Najmul Akhyar）表示地震後大部份地區停電，暫難評估損毀情況。<br />\n一間兒童醫院受損，逾100名病人被迫疏散到戶外，有人坐在輪椅上等候安排。院方在社交網站呼籲各界提供協助，包括供病人暫時棲身的帳篷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/08/06/realtime/5092257.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=800&amp;sh=548&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Frealtime%2F5092257.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D800%26sh%3D548%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=8a128e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/08/06/realtime/5092260.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Frealtime%2F5092260.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=2be1e5c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd970cb6f5a70220357dab62aec8b63b96ac655a","tid":769379,"uid":98232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"真主偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14bff9d1b7a0bdd1f52d1731f33c7eab22c13fe","tid":769379,"uid":90135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"班生番抵撚死"}]}